data.description: Exquisitely maintained Heritage Estates home in highly sought after Mansfield ISD! A beautifully landscaped front yard instantly captivates with blossoming crepe myrtles and a mature oak tree. Step inside to find a spacious floor plan flooded in natural light and custom features. A generously sized office provides a serene area to focus, while the formal dining room serves as the perfect setting for meals with family and friends. The kitchen is a chef’s dream with stainless steel appliances, built-in gas range, and stylish cabinets. Off the breakfast room is a wing with split bedrooms with a flexible living area or den that provides privacy and separation for guests or family members. The master suite is a true retreat boasting an expansive en suite bath and garden tub that promises moments of relaxation and luxury. Outside the backyard offers plenty of space for gathering under the covered patio, and two fans to help keep the Texas heat at bay. Come see it today!
